+-------------------+------------------------------------------------------+</literal_block>
                    <note>
                        <paragraph>By default, IPv6 subnets on provider networks rely on physical network
                            infrastructure for stateless address autoconfiguration (SLAAC) and
                            router advertisement.</paragraph>
                    </note>
                </list_item>
                <list_item>
